OL,16,FWednesday will be sunny and very warm,
OL,17,Fperhaps some patchy coastal haar.
OL,18,FSunny, hot inland Thursday, coastal
OL,19,Fhaar, perhaps some thundery showers
OL,20,Flater. Showery on Friday.
